pokedexEntries.ruby: It is said that through meditation, Medicham heightens energy inside its body and sharpens its sixth sense. This Pokémon hides its presence by merging itself with fields and mountains.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: Through the power of meditation, Medicham developed a sixth sense. It gained the ability to use psychokinetic powers. This Pokémon is known to meditate for a whole month without eating.
pokedexEntries.emerald: Through crushingly harsh yoga training, it gained the power to foretell its foe's actions. It battles with elegant, dance-like movement.
pokedexEntries.fireRed: It elegantly avoids attacks with dance-like steps, then launches a devastating blow in the same motion.
pokedexEntries.leafGreen: It elegantly avoids attacks with dance-like steps, then launches a devastating blow in the same motion.
pokedexEntries.diamond: Through yoga training, it has honed its sixth sense. Its movements are elegant.
pokedexEntries.pearl: Through daily meditation, it hones its spiritual power. It can sense what others are thinking.
pokedexEntries.platinum: It gains the ability to see the aura of its opponents by honing its mind through starvation.
pokedexEntries.heartGold: Through yoga training, it gained the psychic power to predict its foe's next move.
pokedexEntries.soulSilver: Through yoga training, it gained the psychic power to predict its foe's next move.
